dataflowSinks.name: UserQueryDelimitedText1
dataflowSinks.script:
sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	input(
		Invoice_ID as string,
		Branch as string,
		City as string,
		Customer_type as string,
		Gender as string,
		Product_line as string,
		Unit_price as string,
		Quantity as string,
		Tax_5 as string,
		Total as string,
		Date as string,
		Time as string,
		Payment as string,
		cogs as string,
		gross_margin_percentage as string,
		gross_income as string,
		Rating as string
	),
	partitionFileNames:['Pq'],
	truncate: true,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	partitionBy('hash', 1)) ~> UserQueryDelimitedText1
